I added a new section titled "Controversy" to the Kirani Ayat article on Wikipedia. In this section, I highlighted the recent controversy surrounding the unauthorized use of Ayat's music video 'Guda' by the Ghanaian government's tourism industry. I mentioned Ayat's disappointment at the lack of permission and his previous attempts to collaborate with the Ministry of Tourism for promoting tourism in the Northern region using his video.
